    whyCurious: "Colin Dexter, who created Morse, was a regular at the Randolph himself and set many scenes here deliberately. The bar is decorated in a way that makes it feel like being inside a 1980s TV episode. The hotel staff can direct you to exact filming locations in the vicinity — the Ashmolean exterior opposite appeared in the opening credits.",
